---
title: Sweet & Smoky BBQ Glazed Chicken   with Mashed Potatoes & Coleslaw
description: Looking for a way to add tons of extra flavor to your meal? Glaze it up! This delicious savory-sweet glaze comes together in just a few minutes with tangy lemon juice, rich butter, and a luscious swirl of peach jam. Drizzle it over BBQ-seasoned chicken cutlets with sides of creamy mashed potatoes and a classic creamy coleslaw.

